                           <!--Executed mostly in the main hand. On fols. 184r-191v, the first rubricated lines of the Song of Songs’ sections were written in a much hand. Lacunas for the rubricated elements have not been filled on fols. 192ra (the first text line) and fols. 203-208.-->
